leocaseiro:
@oztek22 what's the error are you getting?

If you are using `angular-cli`, try:

```typescript
import { Directive, HostListener } from '@angular/core';
import * as screenfull from 'screenfull';

@Directive({
    selector: '[toggleScreenfull]'
})
export class ToggleScreenfull {
    @HostListener('click') onClick() {
        if (screenfull.enabled) {
            screenfull.toggle();
        }
    }
}
```


Usage:

```
<button toggleScreenfull></button>
